"se *ndigits* for zero, retorna *number* arredondado para o nĂșmero inteiro "
"mais prĂłximo;"

#: ../../library/decimal.rst:965
msgid ""
"if *ndigits* is negative, return *number* rounded to the nearest multiple of "
