msgstr ""
"Um inteiro no intervalo [``1``, :const:`MAX_PREC`] que define a precisĂŁo "
"para operaĂ§Ă”es aritmĂ©ticas no contexto."

#: ../../library/decimal.rst:1128
msgid "One of the constants listed in the section `Rounding Modes`_."
msgstr "Uma das constantes listadas na seĂ§ĂŁo `Modos de arredondamento`_."

#: ../../library/decimal.rst:1133
msgid ""
"Lists of any signals to be set. Generally, new contexts should only set "
