"Traceback (most recent call last):\n"
"  File \"<stdin>\", line 1, in <module>\n"
"  decimal.Inexact: [<class 'decimal.Inexact'>]"

#: ../../library/decimal.rst:2349
msgid ""
"In general (and especially on systems without overallocation), it is "
